snippet.title: Pathfinder Adventures Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore the world of Golarion in the free-to-play version of the acclaimed Pathfinder Adventure Card Game. Out now for Apple iPad and Android Tablets!

Apple: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/pathfinder-adventures/id966333863?mt=8&ign-mpt=uo%3D4

Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=net.obsidian.pacg1
